  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Mix chickpeas with vegan butter or oil, tahini, garlic paste, breadcrumbs, lemon juice, salt, pepper, and chili powder in a mixing bowl.",
    "Add water or milk, stirring until a smooth mixture is formed.",
    "Transfer the mixture to an oven-safe dish. If you prefer it crispier, sprinkle some extra breadcrumbs on top before baking.",
    "Bake for about 20-30 minutes, or until golden brown and crispy on top.",
    "Garnish with lemon zest before serving."
